702084f-a.title: Bronx: Fordham Road (West) - Cedar Avenue
702084f-a.text:
West Fordham Road (running from extreme left center to center back-
ground), east from Cedar Ave., then north to Sedgwick Ave. The thoroughfare
makes a sharp turn northward at Hampden Place. Also shown (foremround) is
the west side of Cedar Ave. running north from West 182nd Street to West
Fordham Road.
1917.
Gift of E.M. Jenks.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
